      <title>SUNAC债权人告诉法院公司没有可行的债务计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/sunac-creditor-tells-court-company-has-no-feasible-debt-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约中国建筑商Sunac China Holdings Ltd.的主要债权人告诉香港法院，该公司尚未为新的海上重组提供任何条款，尽管它旨在遵守此类计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/sunac-creditor-tells-court-company-has-no-feasible-debt-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 06:30:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚中央银行看到了巨大的增长障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/malaysia-central-bank-sees-significant-growth-hurdles-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚中央银行表示，由于酿造全球贸易纠纷和地缘政治紧张局势威胁出口，其货币政策考虑因素在其货币政策方面的考虑巨大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/malaysia-central-bank-sees-significant-growth-hurdles-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
