      <title>南非向国家电网增加800兆瓦的容量单位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/south-africa-adds-800-megawatt-capacity-unit-to-national-grid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家电力公司在库西尔电站增加了一个800兆瓦的单元，这是由于正在进行的努力，以促进产生并结束预定的停电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/south-africa-adds-800-megawatt-capacity-unit-to-national-grid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 06:21:19 GMT</pubDate>
