    <item>
      <title>台湾两年来首次错过了债券销售目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/taiwan-misses-bond-sale-target-for-first-time-in-over-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾自2022年9月以来，由于对唐纳德·特朗普政府的政策的关注，投资者要求在拍卖周一要求更高的收益率，这是自2022年9月以来首次错过了其债券发行的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/taiwan-misses-bond-sale-target-for-first-time-in-over-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 05:55:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当发行人急于击败关税时，亚洲信贷市场升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/asia-credit-market-heats-up-as-issuers-rush-to-beat-tariff-wave</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的下一轮关税的倒计时促使亚太信贷市场上的活动疯狂，并在周一宣布了十多个发行人的营销或宣布美元债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/asia-credit-market-heats-up-as-issuers-rush-to-beat-tariff-wave</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 04:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
